    <h2>The Ultimate Photo Management App</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      Manage all of your photo projects and files from one place. See how Photo App can benefit you!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="row plans">
    <div class="col-sm-5 p-3 text-left">
      <h2>Standard Plan</h2>
      <div class="price pull-top font-weight-bold mb-2">
        Price: $10/month
      </div>
