      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-5 p-3 text-left">
      <h2>Premium Plan</h2>
      <div class="price pull-top font-weight-bold mb-2">
        Price: $20/month
      </div>
      <div class="features">
        <ul>
          <li>Unlimited Image Uploads</li>
          <li>Responsive design</li>
